WEBVTT


00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:17.520
How evil can human nature really get?

00:00:18.280 --> 00:00:19.760
It's like every last one of them is rotten.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:28.799
At least nobody was eating human flesh.

00:00:29.559 --> 00:00:30.760
Now I can finally have a sip of tea.

00:00:37.119 --> 00:00:38.360
What's wrong with all of you?

00:00:39.959 --> 00:00:41.479
Every one of you looks so down.

00:00:41.479 --> 00:00:43.360
Like wilted eggplants.

00:00:45.799 --> 00:00:46.959
What do you do for a living?

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:49.639
You're detectives.

00:00:50.080 --> 00:00:52.599
Criminal Investigation Division, Squad 2.

00:00:53.159 --> 00:00:54.599
What case haven't you solved?

00:00:55.119 --> 00:00:57.000
What kind of human nature is new to you?

00:00:57.119 --> 00:00:58.319
Now pull yourselves together.

00:00:58.959 --> 00:00:59.759
I know.

00:00:59.759 --> 00:01:00.680
These past few days, everyone...

00:01:00.680 --> 00:01:01.959
...has been working a lot of overtime.

00:01:02.439 --> 00:01:03.360
It's been rough.

00:01:03.919 --> 00:01:05.360
Especially you two girls.

00:01:07.199 --> 00:01:08.599
Interrogations really drain you.

00:01:10.319 --> 00:01:11.680
All right, I'll approve it.

00:01:11.839 --> 00:01:14.040
Our squad gets the morning off today.

00:01:15.319 --> 00:01:16.720
Everyone go home.

00:01:17.080 --> 00:01:18.000
All right?

00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:19.440
Pack up and get out of here.

00:01:19.440 --> 00:01:20.680
Especially you two girls.

00:01:20.760 --> 00:01:21.720
Go back and get some rest.

00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:24.199
Captain Duan.

00:01:25.080 --> 00:01:26.239
I'm fine.

00:01:26.239 --> 00:01:27.559
I'm just mentally exhausted.

00:01:27.839 --> 00:01:28.639
What?

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:29.599
Captain.

00:01:30.199 --> 00:01:31.040
I think...

00:01:31.639 --> 00:01:32.879
...we do need to reset a bit.

00:01:33.639 --> 00:01:34.519
Move it, now.

00:01:34.800 --> 00:01:35.919
All of you, get lost.

00:01:36.639 --> 00:01:37.839
Let me be blunt up front.

00:01:38.800 --> 00:01:40.480
When you come back this afternoon...

00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:42.360
...if anyone still looks like this...

00:01:42.919 --> 00:01:44.360
...don't blame me for being ruthless.

00:01:44.839 --> 00:01:45.720
I'll make you

00:01:46.839 --> 00:01:47.879
clean the toilets

00:01:48.760 --> 00:01:49.519
for a month.

00:01:49.519 --> 00:01:50.319
Non-negotiable.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:51.800
Non-negotiable.

00:01:54.319 --> 00:01:55.199
Let's go.

00:01:58.760 --> 00:01:59.559
I'll lead the way.

00:02:00.519 --> 00:02:01.319
Go.

00:02:11.399 --> 00:02:12.199
Let's go.

00:02:12.839 --> 00:02:13.559
Lin Shen.

00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:15.600
Think I should go see Yuan Fei...

00:02:15.600 --> 00:02:16.839
...and have him prescribe some supplements?

00:02:16.839 --> 00:02:18.360
Like vitamins or something, would that work?

00:02:18.360 --> 00:02:20.119
Feels like my brain cells lately...

00:02:20.119 --> 00:02:21.520
...have taken heavy casualties.

00:02:22.279 --> 00:02:23.279
That head of yours...

00:02:24.080 --> 00:02:25.199
...day in, day out...

00:02:25.759 --> 00:02:27.399
...besides money and food...

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:28.880
...can you think about anything else?

00:02:29.559 --> 00:02:31.039
I also think about you.

00:02:36.880 --> 00:02:38.399
I heard that last time we passed

00:02:38.399 --> 00:02:39.559
by that braised-meat shop,

00:02:39.559 --> 00:02:40.520
it was insanely good.

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:42.520
Their pork intestines and head meat...

00:02:43.479 --> 00:02:44.279
...are the real deal.

00:02:44.399 --> 00:02:44.800
Come on.

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:45.600
Let's go right now.

00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:46.839
I can't eat.

00:02:46.839 --> 00:02:48.199
What do you mean you can't eat now?

00:02:48.679 --> 00:02:49.399
Hurry up, let's go.

00:02:49.399 --> 00:02:50.520
We might miss it if we wait.

00:02:50.520 --> 00:02:50.960
Move, now.

00:02:51.919 --> 00:02:52.559
I don't want any.

00:02:52.559 --> 00:02:53.360
I do.

00:02:56.199 --> 00:02:56.919
Come again!

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:57.960
Thanks.

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:00.679
Welcome, you two beauties!

00:03:00.679 --> 00:03:01.399
What'll you have?

00:03:01.399 --> 00:03:01.960
Boss Hu.

00:03:02.119 --> 00:03:03.679
Half a jin of intestines.

00:03:03.679 --> 00:03:04.639
Half a jin of pork head meat.

00:03:04.639 --> 00:03:05.839
And add a bit of this too.

00:03:05.839 --> 00:03:07.320
Bean curd roll and shredded kelp.

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:08.039
Just to fill the gaps.

00:03:08.039 --> 00:03:08.639
That's too much.

00:03:08.639 --> 00:03:09.199
Extra spicy.

00:03:10.039 --> 00:03:10.880
Get her one too.

00:03:10.880 --> 00:03:11.639
Mild is fine.

00:03:11.720 --> 00:03:12.399
Okay, okay, okay.

00:03:12.399 --> 00:03:13.279
I want extra spicy too.

00:03:13.479 --> 00:03:14.080
All right.

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:16.080
Fresh out of the pot, still hot.

00:03:17.600 --> 00:03:18.440
Still want it extra spicy?

00:03:18.559 --> 00:03:19.360
Challenging yourself, huh?

00:03:39.039 --> 00:03:40.360
How'd your watch get this messed up?

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:41.639
And you still won't throw it away?

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:43.720
It was a coming-of-age gift from someone.

00:03:44.240 --> 00:03:45.440
Last time on the street...

00:03:45.600 --> 00:03:46.919
...a motorcyclist hit me.

00:03:47.399 --> 00:03:48.279
My watch fell to the ground...

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:49.199
...and it ended up like this.

00:03:56.520 --> 00:03:56.960
Here.

00:03:57.080 --> 00:03:57.559
This one's spicy.

00:03:57.559 --> 00:03:58.440
This one's not spicy.

00:03:58.479 --> 00:03:59.199
I made them all spicy.

00:03:59.199 --> 00:04:00.000
How much, boss?

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:01.240
A hundred and eight. A hundred is fine.

00:04:01.679 --> 00:04:02.080
Okay.

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:02.800
Come again!

00:04:04.759 --> 00:04:05.399
Hello, boss.

00:04:05.399 --> 00:04:07.080
One order of pork head meat.

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:08.320
How much for the pork head meat?

00:04:08.320 --> 00:04:08.919
One jin.

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:12.119
Here.

00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:13.600
Hold on.

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:19.640
You're really particular.

00:04:32.679 --> 00:04:34.000
These pork intestines...

00:04:34.519 --> 00:04:35.720
...are sliced with the grain.

00:04:49.519 --> 00:04:50.720
This pork head meat...

00:04:50.880 --> 00:04:52.079
...is sliced crosswise.

00:04:59.279 --> 00:05:00.079
Lu Yi.

00:05:02.119 --> 00:05:03.040
Don't chase me.

00:05:03.359 --> 00:05:04.279
What are you doing? Come here.

00:05:04.279 --> 00:05:04.720
Don't come over.

00:05:08.040 --> 00:05:08.880
What's wrong with you?

00:05:10.359 --> 00:05:11.399
You said you wanted to eat.

00:05:11.399 --> 00:05:12.399
But you're not eating at all.

00:05:16.279 --> 00:05:17.079
Lin Shen.

00:05:19.320 --> 00:05:21.079
If it were you...

00:05:21.959 --> 00:05:23.920
...you'd never abandon a friend, right?

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:25.519
Of course.

00:05:30.839 --> 00:05:31.640
Lin Shen.

00:05:34.519 --> 00:05:35.640
That photo...

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:43.000
Lu Yi.

00:05:44.959 --> 00:05:46.200
That photo...

00:05:47.959 --> 00:05:48.760
I...

00:05:55.559 --> 00:05:56.359
Lu Yi.

00:06:20.279 --> 00:06:21.399
Passed by the shop near your place,

00:06:22.079 --> 00:06:22.920
so I brought you a box.

00:06:23.559 --> 00:06:24.239
Thanks.

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:26.399
Treat me to a big meal sometime, okay?

00:06:28.320 --> 00:06:29.079
Lu Yi.

00:06:29.359 --> 00:06:30.720
We haven't seen each other in a while.

00:06:31.600 --> 00:06:32.959
You seem to be in pretty good spirits.

00:06:34.600 --> 00:06:36.679
Made a new friend, huh?

00:06:40.079 --> 00:06:41.239
I'm doing pretty well.

00:06:41.239 --> 00:06:42.920
Isn't it also thanks to Dr. Yuan?

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:43.880
Lately, I

00:06:43.880 --> 00:06:44.760
have been sleeping great.

00:06:44.760 --> 00:06:45.440
So

00:06:45.440 --> 00:06:46.679
I figured I'd come by and see you.

00:06:46.679 --> 00:06:47.920
Then I guess

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:49.040
about that dream of your dad...

00:06:54.480 --> 00:06:55.640
I'll step out.

00:06:56.079 --> 00:06:56.640
No need.

00:06:57.399 --> 00:06:58.519
He's one of us.

00:06:58.679 --> 00:06:59.600
No need to hide anything.

00:07:00.279 --> 00:07:01.079
Hello.

00:07:04.359 --> 00:07:05.440
You really don't hold back, do you?

00:07:06.880 --> 00:07:07.920
Might as well listen.

00:07:10.959 --> 00:07:11.760
Go ahead.

00:07:12.839 --> 00:07:14.200
I think you can

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:15.600
stop taking the meds.

00:07:19.200 --> 00:07:20.519
Where do you think my dad's notebook

00:07:20.519 --> 00:07:21.880
actually went?

00:07:21.880 --> 00:07:23.760
It couldn't just vanish into thin air.

00:07:27.679 --> 00:07:28.440
Honestly,

00:07:28.760 --> 00:07:30.279
When I first met you,

00:07:30.279 --> 00:07:32.040
I really hated your smug attitude.

00:07:32.320 --> 00:07:34.359
Like you'd never been beaten up by life.

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:38.160
A slacker questioning a top student?

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:40.279
What did you score on the fitness test?

00:07:40.559 --> 00:07:41.799
I was the top scorer back in the day.

00:07:42.079 --> 00:07:43.480
I know.

00:07:44.119 --> 00:07:46.160
We're ride-or-die now.

00:07:48.959 --> 00:07:50.200
You just said "one of us."

00:07:50.320 --> 00:07:51.239
Who's "one of us" with you?

00:07:51.839 --> 00:07:53.079
How are you not?

00:07:53.399 --> 00:07:54.440
Otherwise,

00:07:55.160 --> 00:07:57.359
how would I know you grind your teeth?

00:07:57.959 --> 00:07:59.640
Who grinds their teeth? You do!

00:08:00.079 --> 00:08:00.880
And you snore!

00:08:00.880 --> 00:08:01.760
And you fart!

00:08:01.760 --> 00:08:03.160
Who farted?

00:08:03.160 --> 00:08:04.480
You did!

00:08:04.559 --> 00:08:04.880
I'm out.

00:08:04.880 --> 00:08:05.880
I farted?

00:08:05.880 --> 00:08:06.720
I'll stink you to death.

00:08:09.160 --> 00:08:10.079
Officers!

00:08:10.559 --> 00:08:11.640
You're finally here.

00:08:12.079 --> 00:08:12.720
My son.

00:08:12.959 --> 00:08:13.600
My son...

00:08:13.600 --> 00:08:14.399
I...

00:08:14.640 --> 00:08:15.519
Take it slow.

00:08:15.640 --> 00:08:16.320
Take it slow.

00:08:16.600 --> 00:08:18.079
Slow down, slow down.

00:08:19.359 --> 00:08:20.880
My son, Wang Dongdong,

00:08:21.119 --> 00:08:22.480
was kidnapped!

00:08:23.359 --> 00:08:24.519
Mr. Wang, please don't panic.

00:08:24.519 --> 00:08:25.239
Let's take it slowly.

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:26.480
When did you find out

00:08:26.480 --> 00:08:27.600
your son was kidnapped?

00:08:27.920 --> 00:08:29.119
Have the kidnappers contacted you?

00:08:29.200 --> 00:08:30.440
This morning.

00:08:30.559 --> 00:08:32.719
The nanny went to his room to wake him up.

00:08:33.039 --> 00:08:33.840
As soon as she went in,

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:35.400
he was gone.

00:08:35.719 --> 00:08:37.080
The window was open.

00:08:37.280 --> 00:08:39.359
There were signs of struggle on the floor.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.919
Then a call suddenly came in.

00:08:42.200 --> 00:08:43.520
The voice was modified

00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:44.719
with a voice changer.

00:08:45.119 --> 00:08:47.599
They said my son is in their hands.

00:08:47.840 --> 00:08:49.320
They demanded a million in ransom.

00:08:49.479 --> 00:08:51.280
A whole million!

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:53.559
And forbade me from calling the police.

00:08:53.679 --> 00:08:55.599
Or else they'd kill him!

00:08:55.599 --> 00:08:57.440
Have you offended anyone lately?

00:08:58.359 --> 00:09:00.000
For us businessmen,

00:09:00.119 --> 00:09:01.919
how could we not offend someone?

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:02.760
Besides,

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:05.520
Too many people are after my money.

00:09:05.599 --> 00:09:07.599
How could I not have made enemies?

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:08.440
Right.

00:09:08.599 --> 00:09:09.039
Sister Liu.

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:13.599
This

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:15.760
was just delivered this morning.

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:17.320
They said it was my son's.

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:18.400
Dongdong's.

00:09:26.239 --> 00:09:27.159
This is so damn annoying.

00:09:28.159 --> 00:09:29.520
A kidnapping is a kidnapping,

00:09:29.520 --> 00:09:31.320
why'd you have to leave him with one ear?

00:09:35.080 --> 00:09:36.400
Drink less iced stuff these two days.

00:09:36.559 --> 00:09:37.239
Why?

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:38.039
Xiao Lu,

00:09:38.239 --> 00:09:39.440
Your body is your greatest asset.

00:09:39.520 --> 00:09:41.039
If you want to stay healthy, learn from me.

00:09:41.159 --> 00:09:41.960
Captain Duan.

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.039
I'd advise you

00:09:43.039 --> 00:09:45.119
to cut back on your bubble tea.

00:09:45.919 --> 00:09:46.880
Otherwise,

00:09:47.119 --> 00:09:48.599
your blood sugar will beat the suspect

00:09:48.599 --> 00:09:50.119
to reporting to you.

00:09:52.479 --> 00:09:53.400
What's gotten into you?

00:09:56.679 --> 00:09:58.280
Let's talk business.

00:09:58.280 --> 00:09:58.840
Haozi.

00:10:00.159 --> 00:10:01.280
Wang Dahai and his son's relationship,

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:02.280
how's the investigation going?

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:03.840
Found something.

00:10:03.880 --> 00:10:05.320
Wang Dahai's Xinghai Media

00:10:05.320 --> 00:10:06.760
runs an online talent show,

00:10:07.080 --> 00:10:08.280
that's always hit with scandals.

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:09.559
But if they're targeting Wang Dahai,

00:10:09.559 --> 00:10:10.280
then it's very likely

00:10:10.280 --> 00:10:11.840
it's infighting inside his company.

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:12.960
Or else

00:10:13.039 --> 00:10:14.280
some employee he bullied

00:10:14.280 --> 00:10:15.479
couldn't take it anymore

00:10:15.479 --> 00:10:16.520
and came back for revenge.

00:10:16.719 --> 00:10:17.679
People like him

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:19.280
have plenty of enemies.

00:10:19.520 --> 00:10:21.080
And Wang Dongdong's no saint either.

00:10:21.359 --> 00:10:23.119
He drinks, whores, gambles, the works.

00:10:23.640 --> 00:10:24.719
A total spoiled rich kid.

00:10:25.159 --> 00:10:26.479
If he was targeted for his money,

00:10:26.479 --> 00:10:27.159
it's not surprising.

00:10:28.400 --> 00:10:29.080
All right.

00:10:29.359 --> 00:10:30.479
Let's investigate on two tracks.

00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:32.280
Move out.

00:10:32.559 --> 00:10:33.159
Captain.

00:10:34.280 --> 00:10:35.400
The Wang Dahai lead,

00:10:35.799 --> 00:10:36.520
I'll look into it.

00:10:37.320 --> 00:10:37.919
But

00:10:38.119 --> 00:10:40.000
you need to approve some gear for me first.

00:10:40.400 --> 00:10:41.640
So I can go join

00:10:41.640 --> 00:10:43.840
Xinghai's online talent show.

00:10:43.919 --> 00:10:44.919
I'll go see what's up

00:10:44.919 --> 00:10:45.919
with their company.

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:50.119
If that's your reason,

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:52.239
you know full well

00:10:52.440 --> 00:10:54.719
our squad's budget is very tight,

00:10:54.719 --> 00:10:55.599
Right?

00:10:55.799 --> 00:10:56.640
Um,

00:10:57.760 --> 00:10:58.400
Captain Duan.

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:01.799
About the funds,

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:02.679
I'll see what I can do.

00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:20.159
You really are a rich kid.

00:11:20.159 --> 00:11:21.679
Didn't you say you only wear knockoffs?

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.159
Here, hold this.

00:11:27.039 --> 00:11:28.119
Quit messing with me.

00:11:28.119 --> 00:11:28.760
They're all from my family.

00:11:28.760 --> 00:11:29.520
It's not like they're mine.

00:11:33.320 --> 00:11:33.919
Captain.

00:11:34.400 --> 00:11:35.119
Brother Hao.

00:11:35.479 --> 00:11:37.159
This will save us a lot of budget later.

00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:41.760
Captain, who do we give this to?

00:11:42.039 --> 00:11:42.520
Them.

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:51.840
This style.

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:53.760
Doesn't really suit me, does it?

00:11:54.440 --> 00:11:56.080
I'm more of a pool hall type.

00:11:58.520 --> 00:11:59.840
This...

00:12:01.599 --> 00:12:02.400
Lin Shen.

00:12:03.840 --> 00:12:04.679
Why don't you do it?

00:12:05.280 --> 00:12:06.000
Me?

00:12:06.200 --> 00:12:07.159
After you get there,

00:12:07.159 --> 00:12:08.080
tell them

00:12:08.640 --> 00:12:09.880
your family owns a mine,

00:12:10.280 --> 00:12:11.679
you're a rich little lady

00:12:11.679 --> 00:12:13.479
with plenty of free time.

00:12:13.640 --> 00:12:15.080
But your ex-boyfriend,

00:12:15.080 --> 00:12:16.200
to get on this talent show,

00:12:16.200 --> 00:12:17.440
dumped you without a second thought,

00:12:17.719 --> 00:12:18.919
and you're really pissed off,

00:12:19.119 --> 00:12:21.080
so you came to take a look.

00:12:21.359 --> 00:12:22.400
You want to see what magic

00:12:22.400 --> 00:12:23.679
this industry actually possesses.

00:12:24.640 --> 00:12:25.760
And once you're in there,

00:12:26.119 --> 00:12:27.239
you'll treat them

00:12:27.239 --> 00:12:29.400
to good food and drinks,

00:12:29.400 --> 00:12:30.559
so they think you're someone who is

00:12:30.559 --> 00:12:31.880
rich and generous.

00:12:32.239 --> 00:12:33.960
That'll make it easier to get them talking.

00:12:36.159 --> 00:12:36.960
Then what?

00:12:39.479 --> 00:12:40.640
Then...

00:12:42.840 --> 00:12:44.479
Then...

00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:55.799
Is this good?

00:12:56.039 --> 00:12:56.919
Wait a second.

00:13:01.520 --> 00:13:02.359
How is it?

00:13:03.640 --> 00:13:05.080
Is it okay?

00:13:05.400 --> 00:13:07.119
Feels like it's still missing something.

00:13:07.559 --> 00:13:08.599
Still missing...

00:13:08.599 --> 00:13:09.799
What's missing?

00:13:11.320 --> 00:13:12.200
I got it.

00:13:15.799 --> 00:13:17.080
Flaming red lips!

00:13:27.559 --> 00:13:29.200
I feel like you got it in my mouth.

00:13:30.440 --> 00:13:31.640
Don't move.

00:13:40.159 --> 00:13:41.440
How is it? Take a look.

00:13:41.840 --> 00:13:42.320
I'm telling you,

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:43.880
if you walk down the street like this,

00:13:43.960 --> 00:13:45.320
those agents and photographers

00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:46.440
will stare wide-eyed at you.

00:13:46.440 --> 00:13:47.679
And sign you on the spot.

00:13:48.080 --> 00:13:49.440
Don't let this fool you.

00:13:49.760 --> 00:13:52.239
I actually read Xinwei,

00:13:52.239 --> 00:13:53.200
Rayli and all those magazines.

00:13:53.200 --> 00:13:54.080
I'm a fashion expert.

00:13:54.080 --> 00:13:54.880
I'm telling you.

00:13:57.640 --> 00:13:58.440
Let's go.